Description.SourceString: This unique train car has been specially fitted with medical equipment and a mounted machine gun, making it ideal for transporting injured soldiers away from active battlefields to the safety of hospitals. When stationary, the BMS Bloodtender may also be used as a mobile first aid centre to treat wounded soldiers so long as supplies remain plentiful.
